spec: Module name: LPF_st. Module specification: This module implements a Low Pass Filter (LPF) using a symmetric FIR filter structure with 37 taps. Output ports include ready-to-load signal (rdy_to_ld), done signal (done), and 35-bit filtered result (fir_result).
